{"tid":2154066,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文：為港人護蘋動容  「中共圖阻絕人民意志不會成功」","createTime":"2020-08-13T02:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T02:34:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1dba5d6c7e602fc8a40399ab82e7efc80c524c18","tid":2154066,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/KVQWYV2HGI64SPINM5EW2OFR7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FKVQWYV2HGI64SPINM5EW2OFR7Q%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzpa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=32c3d955\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FKVQWYV2HGI64SPINM5EW2OFR7Q%2F&h=329b77aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/KVQWYV2HGI64SPINM5EW2OFR7Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文：為港人護蘋動容 <br />\n「中共圖阻絕人民意志不會成功」<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文昨在出席民進黨中常會前，特意以黨主席身份，就着壹傳媒創辦人黎智英和前香港眾志成員周庭等人被捕一事發表講話。她表示見到港人半夜前往排隊買《蘋果日報》，甚至說連白紙都要買時，為之動容，這是蔡英文在事發後首次就事件公開發表意見。蔡英文指，民進黨作為台灣的執政黨，會堅定支持香港人民爭取自由民主，並且持續提供港人必要的人道協助，促請北京以溝通解決爭議，而不是壓迫人民。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：斥政治檢控如誅九族<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k-7N4Pf-48cOKxQ6dg1k40l10mY=/494x352/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JKGCUETXUOW2K2PTPOA5O7BESI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk-7N4Pf-48cOKxQ6dg1k40l10mY%3D%2F494x352%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJKGCUETXUOW2K2PTPOA5O7BESI.gif&h=297eb758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣民進黨主席蔡英文昨表示會堅定支持香港人民爭取自由民主。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文昨午在舉行民進黨中常會前，特意就黎智英等人被捕發表公開講話。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文說，「香港的情勢如果繼續惡化下去，不僅會造成媒體的寒蟬效應，也。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/psOnKQjwYoCKVoqVU6H_WveKVHc=/889x537/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2EQIWF2FBJHOMPKGN6BATB4R5U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpsOnKQjwYoCKVoqVU6H_WveKVHc%3D%2F889x537%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2EQIWF2FBJHOMPKGN6BATB4R5U.gif&h=63e9f382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方日前大舉搜查壹傳媒激起民憤，大批市民排隊搶購《蘋果日報》以示支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱持續提供人道協助<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文又再一次嚴正呼籲北京當局，應該要想辦法和人民溝通，解決爭議，而不是壓迫人民，剝奪自由和人權。蔡英文說，民進。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，蔡英文昨晚又以台灣總統身份在美國智庫「哈德遜研究所」與「美國進步中心」合辦。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文提到，香港上月的立法會民主派初選縱然受到強權打壓，仍然有成千。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"993516b3233afe7ac644fce04791daaccd0f52de","tid":2154066,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"蔡媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}